<doc id="628401" wikidata="Q7954275" url="?curid=628401" title="WPGH">
<text>WPGH is the call sign of two broadcast stations in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, United States:

*WPGH, the first student radio station at the University of Pittsburgh, which became WPTS-FM in 1986
*WPGH AM, 1080 AM, a radio station which operated in Pittsburgh from 1947 to 1954. The 1080 frequency is currently used by WWNL. 
*WPGH-TV, a television station (channel 20, virtual 53)</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q7954514" start="178" end="185" title="WPTS-FM" label="WPTS-FM"/>
<link wikidata="Q7957388" start="317" end="321" title="WWNL" label="WWNL"/>
<link wikidata="Q7954278" start="325" end="332" title="WPGH-TV" label="WPGH-TV"/>
