* &quot;The Merchant&#x27;s Wife.&quot; Tr. William H. Nienhauser, Jr. In &quot;Modern Chinese Stories and Novellas, 1919–1949.&quot; Eds, Lao, Hsia, Lee. New York: Columbia University Press, 1981, 41–50.
