<doc id="628684" wikidata="Q6654803" url="?curid=628684" title="Live (They Might Be Giants album)">
<text>Live is a 1999 live album by They Might Be Giants. It was a condensed version of &quot;Severe Tire Damage&quot;. While most of the tracks were live, as the name implies, &quot;Doctor Worm&quot; was a studio-recorded track.

